data.description: Home Sweet Home ! Come visit Today ... You Will Be Impressed !!! Open the front door and notice the floor to ceiling Custom rock-work which encases the Cozy fireplace. Custom Wrought Iron Stair Railings. Waterproof vinyl flooring throughout. Brand New energy efficient sliding glass doors leading you out to the private patio and extra storage. Custom brick kitchen backsplash. Custom Stained Decorative Concrete counters in kitchen and half bath. Dual Primary Suites - Each with their own private Full Bath . All of this on a corner lot which offers added privacy. Home backs up to lush Green Space and is surrounded by Large Trees! Walking distance to McAllister Park ; enjoy a walk on the hiking trails or bike around on the numerous bike trails the park has to offer. The location is Incredible...Close proximity to major highways , shopping and airport. Amenity Center offers 2 pools, hot tub and sports courts !! 2 assigned parking spots. Plan your visit Today !
